1. The space HUD owner is `SwgCuiHudSpace`, which installs `SwgCuiHudWindowManagerSpace`; that 
creates:
   - `SwgCuiSpaceRadar` from `RadarPage` at [SwgCuiHudWindowManagerSpace.cpp](D:/Code/swg-client-v2/s
rc/game/client/library/swgClientUserInterface/src/shared/page/SwgCuiHudWindowManagerSpace.cpp:61).
