2/src/game/client/library/swgClientUserInterface/src/shared/page/SwgCuiHudWindowManagerSpace.cpp:83).
   - `SwgCuiShipReticle` binds `SpeedGauge`, `WeaponGauge`, `BoosterGauge`, and reticle images at [Sw
gCuiShipReticle.cpp](D:/Code/swg-client-v2/src/game/client/library/swgClientUserInterface/src/shared/
page/SwgCuiShipReticle.cpp:65).

2. The buggy frame/gauge source resource is `ui_space_gauge_square`.
   - In `ui_hud_space.inc`, the radar/reticle gauge ellipses use 
`SourceResource='ui_space_gauge_square'`, e.g. [line 1678](<D:/Code/SWGSource Client 
v3.0/ui/ui_hud_space.inc:1678>) and [line 2083](<D:/Code/SWGSource Client 
v3.0/ui/ui_hud_space.inc:2083>).
   - No shader prefix means UIManager calls `GetCanvas(empty, textureName)`; colon prefixes only 
split explicit shader names at 
[UIManager.cpp](D:/Code/swg-client-v2/src/external/3rd/library/ui/src/win32/UIManager.cpp:1274).
   - `CuiLayer::TextureCanvas` turns empty shader into `shader/uicanvas_filtered.sht` and texture 
into `texture/ui_space_gauge_square.dds` at [CuiLayer_TextureCanvas.cpp](D:/Code/swg-client-v2/src/en
gine/client/library/clientUserInterface/src/shared/core/CuiLayer_TextureCanvas.cpp:28) and [CuiLayer_
TextureCanvas.cpp](D:/Code/swg-client-v2/src/engine/client/library/clientUserInterface/src/shared/cor
e/CuiLayer_TextureCanvas.cpp:108).

