Code/swg-client-v2/src/engine/client/library/clientGraphics/src/shared/ShaderImplementation.cpp:1533)
. Defaults match the same blend/test defaults at [ShaderImplementation.cpp](D:/Code/swg-client-v2/src
/engine/client/library/clientGraphics/src/shared/ShaderImplementation.cpp:920).

